{"type": "article", "id": 47011, "title": "这套几何图形袜，想解决袜子的落单问题｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2017-11-07T23:08:27Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 45358, "name": "Aēsop"}, {"id": 37569, "name": "Graviky Labs"}, {"id": 929, "name": "乐高"}, {"id": 1270, "name": "Airbnb"}, {"id": 45359, "name": "Helen Konouris"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 6, "praise_count": 73, "image": "img/article/article_show/20171107190218IbHUNd07rORjVqGx.png", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 15.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #323333} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 15.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} p.p5 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #323333} p.p6 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} p.p7 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 12.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #323333} p.p8 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 12.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #323333; min-height: 25.0px} p.p9 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 12.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p10 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font-kerning: none; color: #323333} span.s3 {font-kerning: none; color: #363636} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Solosocks 2.0 by URU Design</h3><p>收衣服或是整理衣柜的时候，难免会发现因为粗心而落单的袜子，但为了凑对把袜子都买成单一颜色的话，搭配起来又太单调了。丹麦设计团队 <a href=\"http://www.uru.dk/\" rel=\"nofollow\">URU Design</a> 想到了一个妙招，干脆让它们本身就不配对——尽管 Solosock 的七款袜子印有不同的几何图形，穿起来并没有太大的违和感，怎么组合都可以。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/solosocks/solosocks-20-a-unique-solution-to-missing-socks\" rel=\"nofollow\">众筹链接</a>，一套的售价从 28 欧元起。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171107190240q4blF25wNJHOcQMR.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.561765\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171107190241hEOISFicTGAa6Wt1.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.864706\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171107190241gaBTs0Duonp98wH3.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.560294\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171107190241Y6qX7vC9yiRZFUz5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.561538\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>The Enigmatic Mind by Aēsop</h3><p>因为实体店<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/tags/2999.html\">室内设计考究</a>被称为“护肤界装修大师”的澳大利亚品牌 <a href=\"http://www.aesop.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Aēsop</a> 最近似乎也想往包装上多做些文章：为今年节日季打造的礼盒系列 The Enigmatic Mind 采用了“社会心理学”这一不太见于护肤品包装的主题，旨在纪念 1950 至 70 年代陆续出现的一系列知名社会心理学实验。整个系列分为六种不同功效的礼盒，设计团队特意将功效和心理学概念一一挂钩，外盒则借鉴了当年社会心理学书籍的装帧。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171107190255jyQNMD8U4d7VoX1W.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171107190255GP5vx2aF0fZ4BQOW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171107190255Dar4SwfpjFyIU6YT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171107190256zR7i6WBhPgXYc0Fm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171107190256LrKi1vpRbQEa9Hos.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Botanical Planter Screens by Helen Konouris</h3><p>想让家里多点绿意，甚至直接用来分隔室内空间的话，墨尔本设计师 <a href=\"http://www.helenkontouris.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Helen Konouris</a> 带来的三款屏风或许是个可行的方法。屏风本身就借鉴了树叶的纹路设计，因此随着藤蔓不断往上生长，它们最终就能还原出一片超大绿叶。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171107190432ogOlDrFtweiG6MTW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201711071904321ZcxFSOtWz2NLmEn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171107190432ZTK98GPzYr5XNIVU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Air Ink scarves by Kelly Gijsen &amp; Graviky Labs</h3><p>如果空气污染物经过处理变得安全，你愿意把它们穿在身上吗？在今年的荷兰设计周上，荷兰设计师 <a href=\"https://kellygijsen.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Kelly Gijsen</a> 带来了一批特殊的围巾。这些围巾所使用的黑色染料由汽车尾气转化为成，由 Gijsen 和印度初创公司 <a href=\"http://www.graviky.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Graviky Labs</a> 合作开发（在此之前，这家公司只推出过用于漆墙的<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/31661.html\">黑色涂料</a>和笔墨）。据悉，这些染料捕捉了 <a href=\"https://www.dezeen.com/2017/11/03/kelly-gijsen-patterns-scarves-using-inks-made-from-pollution-graviky-labs-dutch-design-week/\" rel=\"nofollow\">150 分钟的汽车尾气</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171107190317DRyQVB7l1o4SLxTz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562207\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171107190317CPOeAXyM8kLbJaNS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171107190317jM6zxnpovi5ZBTyL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>LEGO house by LEGO &amp; Airbnb</h3><p>9 月 28 日，乐高体验中心“乐高之家”（LEGO House）正式在乐高诞生的丹麦小城比隆<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/44749.html\">开幕</a>。继品牌旗下的 Architecture 系列推出仅在体验中心销售的<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/44671.html\">建筑模型</a>之后，乐高又与 Airbnb 展开合作，邀请一组家庭入住乐高之家内由 2500 万枚积木构成的乐高房间。值得一提的是，在房间里吃饭前，获胜家庭也要经历一次创造力考验：他们要用积木拼出午餐才能吃到真正的美食。你可以通过<a href=\"https://zh.airbnb.com/night-at/lego-house\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>了解详细情况。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171107190328zgSEpG1wMQPTX3lH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.671149\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171107190328JaoVY4xSnNUrup2l.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.700489\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171107190328NYx8uRl2BsKJwSM3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.687042\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>YamanoteYamanote by Julien Mercier &amp; Julien Wulff</h3><p>当你和你的设计师朋友都想为自己喜欢的城市做些什么的时候，或许就会诞生像是 <a href=\"http://yamanoteyamanote.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">YamanoteYamanote</a> 这样有趣的项目。现居东京的瑞士人 Julien Mercier 和 Julien Wulff 同为平面设计师，他们以当地著名的山手线为灵感，根据 29 个车站附近的街景分别创作一张海报。目前，他们已经完成了 11 个车站的海报，如果你感兴趣的话还可以通过 <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/yamanoteyamanote/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Instagram</a> 关注进展。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171107190345gOaZA8TKGoJ6xVri.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667442\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171107190346e25PpESvs8JWxD1C.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171107190346aOGEx3K7jJnf4diT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666279\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171107190346RgS2scmUZM4KTLvC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666279\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}